	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=148048><span id= >deethleech</span></a><br><span id=notbold>74 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.24]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I got this sword just tonight and it's hard to say if it is better then my Greatstaff of the Four Winds or not.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's a good weapon until you start hitting ele planes or can get the hammer from VZ no doubt.  The proc doesn't go off near as much as my staff proc does, it seems I am lucky to get it to go off 1-2 per fight when i solo.. once in awhile 3, quite a bit 0.  Don't count on the proc to keep you alive.  It's definetly fast and seems easier to hold agro with, though the stats and hp on it are kinda low.  Looks like the little graphic from link does.  All in all not a bad weapon, only wish it had some ac and maybe proced more.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
